"Flatpak will export the following desktop filename patterns: "
"``$FLATPAK_ID.desktop, $FLATPAK_ID.foo.desktop, $FLATPAK_ID-"
"foo.desktop``. Exported desktop files can be found in the "
"``applications`` subfolder of "
